channel.title: Privates on Scott O'Brien
channel.description: Recent content in Privates on Scott O'Brien

item.description: Night of the 16th: Start developing headaches, chills and muscle soreness Lots and lots of sleep as body felt exhausted Cleared up, felt good for the weekend Tuesday 23: Started with coughs and lots of phlegm in lungs Lots of exhaustion, coughing and sleep right through to 27th. Covid test returned negative result Saturday 27th: Started throat soreness after coughing a bit, assumed I had torn my throat Noticed it was worse the next morning and has been getting progressively worse since.
